{"tid":453410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【恫嚇閉門作賽又不成】亞洲足協就噓國歌事件對香港足總發警告","createTime":"2017-10-31T07:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T07:18:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a18e76e083e6a7d49aec6862b23c7bf261be279","tid":453410,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"今次錢都無罰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362249-20171031.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362249-20171031.htm&d=buFYMUadxM7cOVM0KOViTBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=60612afd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362249-20171031.htm&h=4e23af35\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362249-20171031.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n對於本月在大球場舉行港足對馬來西亞的亞洲盃外圍賽時，有香港球迷噓國歌的事件，亞洲足協裁定，對香港足總發出警告。<br />\n<br />\n亞洲足協紀律和道德委員會上星期五開會討論，認為香港球迷的行為違反規例，若再違規可能會處以更嚴重懲罰。"},{"pid":"10c28c29609cee6654f0c3453ea5a5e0e5cde514","tid":453410,"uid":37297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"嚇死人咩 個心離一離呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ec1386c1caea86b0eaf616499b79b89619e2a7","tid":453410,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"咁都閉門真係國際笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}